{"tha-ap61:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap61:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap61:0.3":"Padumattheraapadana ","tha-ap61:1.1":"“Catusaccam pakasento, ","tha-ap61:1.2":"varadhammappavattako; ","tha-ap61:1.3":"Vassate amatam vutthim, ","tha-ap61:1.4":"nibbapento mahajanam. ","tha-ap61:2.1":"Sadhajam padumam gayha, ","tha-ap61:2.2":"addhakose thito aham; ","tha-ap61:2.3":"Padumuttaramunissa, ","tha-ap61:2.4":"pahattho ukkhipimambare. ","tha-ap61:3.1":"Agacchante ca padume, ","tha-ap61:3.2":"abbhuto asi tavade; ","tha-ap61:3.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap61:3.4":"pagganhi vadatam varo. ","tha-ap61:4.1":"Karasetthena paggayha, ","tha-ap61:4.2":"jalajam pupphamuttamam; ","tha-ap61:4.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap61:4.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap61:5.1":"‘Yenidam padumam khittam, ","tha-ap61:5.2":"sabbannumhi vinayake; ","tha-ap61:5.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap61:5.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap61:6.1":"Timsakappani devindo, ","tha-ap61:6.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap61:6.3":"Pathabya rajjam sattasatam, ","tha-ap61:6.4":"vasudham avasissati. ","tha-ap61:7.1":"Tattha pattam ganetvana, ","tha-ap61:7.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap61:7.3":"Akasato pupphavutthi, ","tha-ap61:7.4":"abhivassissati tada. ","tha-ap61:8.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap61:8.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap61:8.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap61:8.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap61:9.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap61:9.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap61:9.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap61:9.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap61:10.1":"Nikkhamitvana kucchimha, ","tha-ap61:10.2":"sampajano patissato; ","tha-ap61:10.3":"Jatiya pancavassoham, ","tha-ap61:10.4":"arahattam apapunim. ","tha-ap61:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap61:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap61:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap61:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma padumo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap61:13.1":"Padumattherassapadanam navamam. "}